<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ dāng wǒ shī luò de shí hòu, nǐ shì tǔ rǎng. zhǔ dāng wǒ mí shī de shí hòu, nǐ shì fāng xiàng.
 wú chù ān xiē de shí hòu, nǐ shì bì fēng gǎng. wǒ hěn lèi hěn lèi, jiù lái dào nǐ shēn páng.
 zhǔ a wǒ zhī dào, nǐ shì wǒ de lì liàng. duō shǎo cì fēng shuāng xuě yǔ, hán lái shǔ wǎng.
 nǐ dōu ān wèi yǐn dǎo, nǐ de zhàng nǐ de gān, nǐ shì wǒ yī shēng de lì liàng.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ de lì liàng 迦南912</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
